data.description: Priced to Sell!   Nice Brick/Vinyl Ranch home.  Just need a little TLC.  Property located close to golf course, local park, Wssu and highway access.  Property Consist of nice back yard, Patio, some hardwood floors, one car garage and washer/dryer connection.  Property being Sold as-is.  The heating/Cooling unit needs replacing, and the Electrical panel / wiring needs to be replaced.  Agents see agent only remarks. Interior Pics coming soon
